detail_desc: Sleeveless dress in a patterned cotton weave with a V-neck at the back and buttons down the back. Gathered seam and decorative bow at the waist and a flared skirt. Unlined.
Long-sleeved jumper in jacquard-knit cotton with a hood with a pompom on top, and ribbing around the cuffs and hem.
Jumper in a soft, jacquard-knit cotton blend with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Shirt in soft Oxford cotton with a button-down collar, classic front and yoke with a pleat and hanger at the back. Open chest pocket, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back. Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently tapered waist to create a comfortable, tailored silhouette.
Sports bra in fast-drying functional fabric. V-neck with a mesh detail front and back, removable inserts, double narrow shoulder straps and a racer back. Elastic hem. Medium support.
Ballet pumps with a decorative elastic bow on the front with metal tips. Satin linings, imitation leather insoles and smooth soles.
Long-sleeved top in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a print motif, jersey-lined hood and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with anti-slip protectors.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in organic cotton denim with an extra-high waist, zip fly and button, and extra-wide legs that taper to the hems.

Set with a shirt, sweater vest and bow tie or tie. Shirt in a cotton weave with a narrow turn-down collar, buttons down the front and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs. V-neck sweater vest in fine-knit cotton with ribbed trims. Pre-tied tie/bow tie with an adjustable elastic strap and plastic fastener at the back.

Set with a top and pair of shorts in soft cotton jersey. Top with appliqués on the front and flounced sleeves that continue down the sides. Shorts with a decorative bow at the front, an elasticated waist with a small frill trim at the top and diagonal side pockets.
Short-sleeved romper suit in soft, patterned organic cotton jersey with buttons down the front and concealed press-studs at the crotch and down the legs.
Short dress in a soft jacquard weave with short flounced sleeves, a V-neck and gathers at the shoulders. Narrow elasticated seam under the bust with a frill trim and ties. Partly lined.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend.
CONSCIOUS Joggers in organic cotton sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.

Set containing nine earrings and two ear cuffs in metal. Five pieces are decorated with glass rhinestones. Three of the earrings are hoops with small pendants. The zinc and brass content are recycled.
Top in soft sweatshirt fabric with a kangaroo pocket, jersey-lined hood with a wrapover front, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Long skirt in jacquard-weave mesh with wide elastication at the waist. Jersey underskirt.
Joggers in sturdy cotton piqué with an elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets, a fake welt back pocket and ribbed hems.
Round-necked T-shirt in soft cotton jersey.
Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated, drawstring waistband, side pockets and rounded hems. Contrasting colour stripes and trims at the sides and hems.
Leggings in stretch, printed cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.
Sleeveless dress in a patterned cotton weave with a small V-neck at the back of the neck and buttons at the back. Gathered seam at the waist and a decorative bow at the front. Unlined.
Make-up bag a zip at the top that continues down the short sides. Lined. Size approx. 7x11.5x18.5 cm.
Slip-on, fabric trainers with elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the back. Canvas linings and insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles.
Double-layered hat in a soft rib knit with a sewn-in turn-up at the hem with a small fabric appliqué on the front.
Straight-cut jacket in a striped cotton weave with narrow notch lapels, jetted front pockets and long sleeves with a tab and button. No fasteners. Unlined.
Short, straight-cut dress in a slub-weave modal blend with a small, frilled collar, opening with narrow ties at the top and short sleeves. Unlined.
Sports top in fast-drying functional fabric with a racer back.
Cap with a sweatband in a cotton weave and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Straight-cut dress in a soft weave with a V-neck and small stand-up collar. Dropped shoulders, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back. Unlined.
Long-sleeved shirt in a cotton weave with a button-down collar and buttons down the front.
Sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with ventilating mesh sections and a concealed drawstring at the waist with a key pocket in the waistband.
Cropped top in light sweatshirt fabric with a print motif. Dropped shoulders, long, wide sleeves with ribbed cuffs and raw-edge hem.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed denim with hard-worn details, in  a loose fit with a high waist, zip fly and button, low crotch and straight  legs with raw-edge hems.

Short dress in woven fabric with a round neckline and opening with a button at the back of the neck. Dropped shoulders, short, double-layered flounced sleeves and a detachable tie belt at the waist. Lined.

Windbreaker in nylon with a detachable hood, zip and wind flap with press-studs down the front and long raglan sleeves. Welt front pockets with a press-stud, elasticated cuffs and a drawstring at the hem. Lined.
Mesh trainers with a padded edge and tongue, lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and ethylene-vinyl acetate (EVA) and rubber soles.

Oversized shirt woven in a linen blend with a collar and V-neck with a pleat at the front. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves with buttons at the cuffs, a yoke with a pleat at the back and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Vest top in cotton jersey with a print motif.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with high shafts and elasticated tops.
Fitted top in transparent, printed, stretch mesh with a small stand-up collar, visible seams and long sleeves with thumbholes at the cuffs.
Lightly padded, fleece-lined all-in-one suit with a lined hood, buttons at the top and concealed press-studs at the sides.
Brazilian briefs in microfibre and mesh with a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and half-string back.
Slightly boxy jumper knitted in a soft, fluffy wool blend with dropped shoulders, long, wide sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Socks in a fine knit containing glittery threads.
Velour backpack with faux fur pompoms, a zip and handle at the top, adjustable imitation leather shoulder straps and zipped outer pocket. Lined. Size 11x24x27 cm.
Jumper in a soft, fine-knit viscose blend with a brushed finish. Long sleeves with lace sections, and sewn-on lace appliqués at the top and on the elbows.
Hipster briefs in cotton jersey with a lined gusset.

STUDIO COLLECTION. Wide, boxy, hooded top in printed, cotton sweatshirt fabric. Stand-up collar with a drawstring, low dropped shoulders with seams, and long, wide dolman sleeves with raw, roll edges and slits at the cuffs. Wide ribbing at the hem and slits in the sides. Longer at the back.
Calf-length dress in a patterned modal and cotton weave with a V-neck and short sleeves. Gathered seam under the bust and at the back, and an asymmetric skirt. Lined.
Card holder in grained imitation leather with two compartments on each side and one compartment at the top. Height 7 cm. Width 10 cm.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft, fine cotton knit with a rounded hem and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Slightly longer at the back.

Long, flared dress in a patterned weave. Narrow cut at the top with a slim band at the neckline, an opening with a hook-and-eye fastening at the back of the neck and a seam and wide flounce at the hem. Satin lining.

Calf-length dress woven in an airy viscose blend with a collar, buttons down the front, yoke at the back and chest pockets. Gently dropped shoulders, 3/4-length, wide sleeves with buttoned cuffs, an elasticated waist and gently flared skirt. Unlined.

Loafers in imitation leather with a decorative bow and moccasin seam at the front and a decorative welt seam around the soles. Twill linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Heel approx. 2 cm.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a press-stud on one shoulder.

Jacket in washed denim with a pile collar and press-studs down the front. Welt side pockets, a flap chest pocket with a press-stud, adjustable tabs with press-studs at the sides and press-studs at the cuffs. Pile lining.
Short jersey top with a V-neck, short sleeves, decorative buttons and a tie detail at the front and an elasticated hem.
Short, wide blouse in woven fabric with a collar, buttons down the front, gathers at the shoulders, short cap sleeves and a rounded hem. Trims down the side seams and around the hem.

Blouse in an airy weave with a small stand-up collar, V-neck, button placket and chest pocket. Gathered yoke at the shoulders and back, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Hipster briefs in cotton jersey with lace trims, a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and cutaway coverage at the back.
Straight-cut jersey top with short sleeves that end in flounces in woven fabric.
Thong briefs in microfibre and mesh with a low waist, decorative straps at the top, a lined gusset, narrow sides and string back. The briefs are made partly from recycled polyamide.
Off-the-shoulder blouse in woven fabric with an elasticated top with a small frill trim, narrow tie-top shoulder straps and short, wide sleeves.

High-waisted, ankle-length sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric. Wide panel to hold in and shape the waist containing a concealed key pocket. Sculpting seams at the back that showcase the body’s physique.
Jersey-lined joggers in stretch, supersoft denim with an elasticated drawstring waist, a back pocket, side pockets and tapered legs.

Cropped, sleeveless sports top in fast-drying functional fabric with a small stand-up collar and racer back. Integral sports bra with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support, and an elasticated hem.
Metal hoop earrings in various sizes.

Wide, airy blouse in a patterned viscose weave with a wide collar that ties at the front, and buttons at the top. Yoke with gathers at the shoulders and back, long, wide sleeves, and cuffs with covered buttons.
T-shirts in soft cotton jersey.
Baby Exclusive. Leggings in soft, lightweight wool jersey with an elasticated waist.
KIDS EXCLUSIVE. Leggings in a soft, rib-knit organic cotton blend with covered elastication at the waist and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Blouse in softly draping silk with a small frilled collar with ties at the front. Opening at the top, long sleeves with narrow cuffs and a covered button, and a rounded hem.
Cotton jersey T-shirt with a deep, raw-edge neckline and short sleeves with raw edges.
Socks in a soft, fine, fluffy knit containing glittery threads. Elasticated at the top.
Blouse in a viscose weave with a collar and buttons down the front. Yoke with a pleat at the back, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Fine-knit gloves with matching fingerless gloves. The gloves can be worn over each other or separately.

Lined, non-wired, triangle bikini top with a wide hem. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps that can be fastened in different ways at the back and cups with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. No fasteners.
Double-layered tube scarf in soft cotton jersey.
Bikini briefs in organic cotton jersey with a mid waist, lined gusset and medium coverage at the back.
Brazilian briefs in lace with a narrow decorative trim at the top. Mid waist, lined gusset and high cut at the back.
Lace bra with underwired, lightly padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. Wide, adjustable shoulder straps and a fastening at the back with three pairs of hooks and eyes.
Linen joggers with a regular, elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets, a fake back pocket and tapered legs.
Short-sleeved jumper in a fine, striped knit with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Top in a cotton weave with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps. Tie at the top, gathered seam at the waist, zip in the side and a flare to the hem.

Short, fitted underdress in microfibre with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and an inner top with opening cups with space for nursing pads. The dress is designed with the minimum number of seams for a more comfortable fit and increased mobility. Can be used both during pregnancy and when nursing afterwards.
Jacquard-knit socks in various colours and designs.
Jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Lace push-up bra with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a wide hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Knee-length dress in jersey crêpe and lace with a round neckline and cap sleeves. Seam at the waist, a concealed zip at the back, and a gently flared skirt.
Short-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front (normal sequins in size 2-3Y). Rounded and slightly longer at the back.
Lightly padded, thermal gilet with a lined hood, zip down the front, side pockets and a zipped chest pocket. Lined.
Hat in a soft cable knit with a rib-knit fold-up hem.
Straight-cut, off-the-shoulder blouse in an airy cotton weave with elastication at the shoulders, buttons at the front and 3/4-length balloon sleeves with cuffs.

5-pocket, ankle-length trousers in imitation leather with an extended waistband and concealed button. Side pockets, welt back pockets with a button, zip fly and concealed hooks and eyes. Straight legs in a slightly looser fit with seams at the knees.
Short-sleeved shirt in a patterned viscose weave with a resort collar, French front and short slits in the sides.
Jeans in washed, stretch denim with fake front pockets, real back pockets and super-skinny legs. Wide jersey panel at the waist for best fit over the tummy.
Hair elastics with bows and shiny plastic beads at the ends. No metal clips.
Top in block-coloured sweatshirt fabric with a lined drawstring hood with a wrapover front. Kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Trunks in stretch cotton jersey with flatlock seams, an elasticated waist, lined front and short legs.
Tunic in woven fabric with a collar, buttons down the front, side pockets and a belt. Long sleeves with a tab and button, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit with an embroidered motif on the turned-up hem.
Chelsea boots in imitation leather with a soft, stretchy shaft and loop at the back. Jersey linings, imitation leather insoles and chunky soles. Heel 5 cm.

Baby Exclusive. Dungarees in soft, organic cotton corduroy with buttons at the sides and straps with adjustable buttoning at the front. Elastication at the back of the waist, and elasticated hems. Concealed press-studs at the crotch and down the legs (except in sizes 1½-4Y). Lined at the top.
Cardigan in a soft knit containing some wool with gently dropped shoulders and long sleeves. Front pockets, ribbing at the cuffs and hem and no buttons.

Knee-length dress in soft jersey with a wrapover top that has a practical inner top for easier nursing access. Long sleeves, and elasticated seam at the waist and a skirt with a sewn-in wrapover. Unlined.
T-shirt in soft jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front and narrow ribbing around the neckline.

Ankle-length dress in a cotton weave with lace details, a V-neck, narrow adjustable shoulder straps and a concealed zip at the back. Seam under the bust with pleats and a lace trim, and a seam at the hem with a lace trim and wide, pleated flounce. Lined at the top and with a short underskirt.
Vest top in soft, fast-drying mesh jersey with a racer back.
Fitted shirt in a stretch weave made from a cotton blend with a collar and concealed buttons down the front. Chest pocket, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a gently rounded hem.
Baby Exclusive. T-shirt in soft organic cotton slub jersey with a button placket and short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups.
Fully lined bikini top with hole-patterned, underwired, moulded, padded cups that lift and shape, and ties at the back of the neck.
Fine-knit polo shirt in a silk and cotton blend with a button placket and ribbing at the collar, cuffs and hem.
Sleeveless top in printed cotton jersey with a frill around the armholes.
Ankle-length skirt in an airy silk and cotton blend. High, gathered waist with covered elastication and a seam lower down the skirt with narrow, gathered smocking for added volume. Unlined.
Push-up bra in microfibre and lace with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a narrow hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Slightly shorter top in soft cotton jersey with long sleeves and overlocked edges at the cuffs and hem.
Cropped top in soft jersey with lace details, a V-neck and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.
Short dress in an airy weave with an opening at the top and small, pleated stand-up collar with ties at the front. Short, pleated cap sleeves and a narrow, elasticated seam at the waist. Lined.
3/4-length leggings in soft organic cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.

Short-sleeved boiler suit in cotton twill with notch lapels and concealed buttons down the front. Flap chest pockets, a seam at the waist with a soft tie belt, front pockets and gently tapered legs with covered elastication at the hems.
Slim-fit trousers in stretch twill. High waist with adjustable elastication (in sizes 8-12Y), a zip fly and button, back pockets and narrow hems.

Ankle-length trousers in twill made from a cotton blend. High paper bag waist with pleats and a detachable tie belt, a zip fly and buttons, diagonal side pockets with a decorative flap and button, and tapered legs.
Baby Exclusive. Elastic hairbands in a soft organic cotton weave with a decorative knot detail at the front.
Headband in a soft knit containing some wool with a draped detail at the front. Width approx. 11.5 cm.
Short skirt in woven fabric with a high waist and zip at the back.

Jacket in cotton denim with a collar, buttons down the front and at the cuffs, flap chest pockets with a button and diagonal welt pockets at the bottom. Yoke at the top and a tab with adjustable buttoning at the sides.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft, textured-knit cotton blend with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Microfibre slip with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.
Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated, drawstring waistband, side pockets and rounded hems. Contrasting colour stripes and trims at the sides and hems.
Long earrings in metal and plastic. Length 11.5 cm.
Jumper in a soft, fine-knit wool blend with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fine-knit trainer socks in a soft cotton blend with elasticated tops.

Single-breasted jacket in a linen weave with narrow notch lapels, a decorative buttonhole and two buttons at the front. Chest pocket, welt front pockets and two inner pockets. Decorative buttons at the cuffs and a single back vent. Partly lined. Slim Fit – a fit that tapers at the chest and waist, which combined with slightly narrower sleeves creates a fitted silhouette.
Dungaree dress in stretch cotton twill with adjustable straps that join at the back. Metal fasteners on the straps, front pockets and press-studs at the sides.
Shirt in a cotton weave with a collar, buttons down the front and a contrasting colour on the inside of the collar stand and cuffs. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Fine-knit trainer socks with an embroidered motif and elasticated tops.
Thong briefs in lace with a low waist and lined gusset.
Leggings in soft organic cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.
All-in-one pyjamas in soft, patterned velour. Concealed zip down the front with a chin guard and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hems.
Swim shorts in a patterned weave with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and a back pocket with a hook and loop fastening. Mesh inner shorts.
5-pocket slim-fit jeans in supersoft, stretch denim with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and legs with seams and narrow hems.

Fully lined bikini top with a tie detail at the front, underwired, thickly padded cups to maximise the bust and create a fuller cleavage, ties at the back of the neck and a metal fastener at the back.

Shirt in an airy, slub cotton weave with a grandad collar, buttons down the front and yoke with a pleat at the back. Chest pocket, long sleeves with a tab and button, buttoned cuffs, and a gently rounded hem.
Short, fitted sports top in fast-drying functional fabric with a round neck and short sleeves.
Tights in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with an elasticated waist.
Fitted top in heavily draping ribbed jersey made from a viscose blend with short sleeves. Ribbed trims around the neckline, sleeves and hem.
Sports trousers in fast-drying functional fabric with a wide, drawstring waistband and cuffed hems.

Ankle-length sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with jacquard-patterned details. High waist with a wide, elasticated waistband. The tights are designed with the minimum number of seams for a more comfortable fit and increased mobility.
Long-sleeved top in soft jersey with a flounce at the front that continues along the sleeves.
5-pocket shorts in washed, stretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button and raw-edge, cut-off hems.
Polo shirt in cotton piqué with a collar, button placket, short puff sleeves with ribbed trims, and short slits in the sides. Small embroidery detail at the front.
Soft slippers with elastication around the opening and soft, imitation leather soles.
Top in printed sweatshirt fabric made from a soft cotton blend with long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Soft, non-wired, lace nursing bra with lightly padded, opening cups with space for nursing pads. Adjustable shoulder straps and a wide hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Fabric cap with an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.

Push-up bra in lace with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow adjustable shoulder straps that cross at the back and a narrow fastening at the back with two pairs of hooks and eyes.
Sunglasses with metal and plastic frames and tinted, UV-protective lenses.
Pouch bag with a grained imitation leather top and transparent bottom to allow an easy overview of contents. Zip with a practical tab at the top. Width approx. 1.5 cm. Height 17 cm. Length 23 cm.
Knee-length dress in a fine knit with a slight sheen. Short cap sleeves, a seam at the waist, and a flared, pleated skirt. Unlined.
Scarves in patterned satin that can also be tied as a hairband. Size 30x80 cm.
Sports shorts in fast-drying functional fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist and reflective detail.
Sleeveless dress in printed viscose jersey with frill trims around the armholes and an elasticated seam with a wide flounce at the hem. Unlined.
Long metal necklace with sparkly stones. Adjustable length approx. 52-59 cm.
All-in-one pyjamas in patterned stretch cotton jersey with press-studs down the front and ribbing at the cuffs and hems.

Set with a T-shirt and pair of shorts in soft, printed cotton. T-shirt in jersey with a press-stud on one shoulder (except in sizes 1½-4Y). Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated, drawstring waist, side pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Fitted T-shirt in ribbed jersey made from a silk and viscose blend with a round neck and short sleeves.
Patterned bikini. Lined, off-the-shoulder top with covered elastication and flounces at the top. Fully lined bottoms.
Shorts in soft, patterned sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets.
Short, pleated skirt in a patterned weave with a high waist with covered elastication. Rounded hem that is shorter at the sides. Unlined.
Striped jersey T-shirt in a cotton blend.

Lace bra with underwired, moulded, lightly padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. Decorative straps at the front, narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a fastening at the back with three pairs of hooks and eyes.
Calf-length skirt in a softly draping viscose weave. High, frill-trimmed waist with covered elastication and decorative buttons at the front, and side pockets. Longer at the back. Unlined.
Bustier in a patterned weave with shoulder straps, a concealed zip in one side and decorative lacing at the back. Jersey lining.
Straight-cut dress in a patterned weave with short sleeves. Unlined.
5-pocket shorts in sturdy washed denim with a high waist, zip fly and button, and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Sun visor in braided paper straw with a sweatband in woven fabric. Sewn-on ears at the top, embroidery on the visor and a hook and loop fastening at the back.
Cap in woven fabric with a motif on the front and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Boxy-style T-shirt in printed cotton jersey with narrow ribbing around the neckline.

Pyjamas with a strappy top and bottoms in soft jersey made from a cotton blend. V-neck top with a lace trim at the top and narrow adjustable shoulder straps. Bottoms with an elasticated waist and straight, wide legs with lace-trimmed hems.
Long-sleeved dress in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with a hole pattern at the top, gathered seam at the waist and flared skirt with a lace trim at the hem. Unlined.
Airy top with a small frilled collar and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Short sleeves with a flounce at the ends, and a seam at the hem with a wide flounce on one side.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a round neckline, glittery print on the front and a rounded hem.
Baby Exclusive. Cardigan in soft, fine-knit organic cotton with a round neck and buttons down the front.

Short dress in an airy weave made from a Tencel™ lyocell blend containing some linen. Stand-up collar with a V-shaped opening and wide ties at the front. Wide, 3/4-length raglan sleeves, narrow cuffs with adjustable buttoning, and a gathered seam at the hem for added width.
USB 2.0 charging cable suitable for iPhones 6/7/8 PLUS/X. Length 1 m. The cable is only for charging and synchronisation via a computer.
Patterned swimsuit with flounce-trimmed shoulder straps.
Sleeveless bodysuits in soft organic cotton jersey with press-studs at the crotch.
Off-the-shoulder blouse in an airy viscose weave with broderie anglaise. Smocking at the top,long sleeves and elasticated cuffs with a flounce.
Short skirt in imitation leather with decorative seams and a visible zip at the back. Lined.
Ankle-length leggings in sturdy jacquard-patterned jersey. Regular waist with concealed elastication and slim legs.
Twill trousers with a concealed zip in the side, welt back pockets and asymmetric, flounced hems.
Jumper in a soft fine cotton knit with buttons on one shoulder, raglan sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric with a motif on the front, ribbed turtleneck, dropped shoulders and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Longer jacket woven in a viscose blend with a shawl collar, pockets in the side seams and 3/4-length sleeves with a slit at the cuffs. Lined.
Straight-cut T-shirt in a soft modal and cotton blend with a round neckline and shoulder pads.
Ribbed vest top in soft, organic cotton jersey with a lace trim around the neckline and armholes and an overlocked hem.
Hipster briefs in cotton jersey with a mid waist, lined gusset, wide sides and medium coverage at the back.
Pyjamas in soft satin. V-neck top with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and frills at the top. Short shorts with an elasticated waist and frilled hems.

Padded jacket in woven fabric with a sheen. Lined drawstring hood, zip down the front, side pockets with a concealed hook and loop fastening and one inner pocket. Ribbing at the cuffs and hem and a quilted lining in a contrasting colour. Polyester filling.

Twill suit trousers in a wool blend with a zip fly, concealed hook-and-eye fastener, side pockets, welt back pockets and flap leg pockets. Slim fit that is close-fitting at the thighs, knees and ankles to create a fitted silhouette.
Trainers in imitation leather with a padded edge and tongue, and lacing at the front. Mesh linings and insoles and patterned soles.
Metal ball chain necklace with a plastic pendant in the shape of a skeleton hand that glows in the dark. Length 45 cm.
Coat in soft, felted fabric with a detachable lined hood, rounded collar and buttons down the front. Front pockets with a decorative flap and pleated back. Lined.
Calf-length dress in a patterned viscose weave with a collar, buttons down the front, and long, wide sleeves with buttoned cuffs. Narrow elastication and a detachable tie belt at the waist. Unlined.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit containing glittery threads with a reversible sequin motif.
Long top in soft sweatshirt fabric with reversible sequins, a wrapover hood, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Joggers in sweatshirt fabric with elasticated ribbing at the waist, pockets in the side seams and ribbed hems.
Fully lined bikini top with padded cups, wide shoulder straps that cross at the back, and a plastic fastener at the back.
Leather belt with a metal buckle. Width 2.9 cm.
Wide blouse in an airy viscose weave with a grandad collar, gathers and buttons down the front, low dropped shoulders and long, cuffed sleeves.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine-knit wool and cashmere blend with a turned-up hem.
Sun hat in a cotton weave with ties under the chin. Lined. Width of brim 4.5 cm.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem, and slits in the sides.
Sports shorts in fast-drying functional fabric with a regular elasticated, drawstring waist, mesh key pocket in the waistband and short slits at the hems.
High-waisted jeans in washed superstretch denim with a zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and super-skinny legs.
5-pocket, high-waisted jeans in washed stretch denim with worn details, a zip fly and button and skinny legs.

Sleeveless dress in tulle with narrow shoulder straps, a sequined bodice and a zip at the back. Gathered seam at the waist and a super-flared skirt in two layers of tulle, the top layer with sequined butterfly appliqués. Lined.
Trousers in soft viscose jersey with an elasticated waist, side pockets and wide, tapered legs with elasticated hems.
